                  "content": "OVERVIEW\nAudio/video editor built around transcript editing.\n\nCORE PRODUCT\nTranscription, editing, screen capture, export.\n\nPOSITIONING\nCreator-first production workflow.\n\nSTRENGTHS\nEditing depth, creator familiarity.\n\nLIMITATIONS\nCan feel heavier than lightweight summarizers.\n\nPRICING MODEL\nSubscription tiers.\n\nTARGET AUDIENCE\nPodcasters, editors, creator teams.",
