                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "sn0Q6",
                              "name": "summaryBody",
                              "fill": "#1F2937",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "# Business Idea Summary\n\n## Core Concept\nA local gourmet bakery service selling curated mini dessert boxes (brownies, cookies, and other mini desserts) for gifting, birthdays, events, and corporate orders, delivered via local pickup and same-day/local delivery with future expansion to scheduled corporate bulk fulfillment.\n\n## Problem Statement\nCustomers need attractive, ready-to-gift dessert solutions without the time, skill, or coordination of sourcing multiple items. Businesses need reliable, branded gifting options for employees and clients. This saves time, reduces event planning friction, and provides a memorable, edible gift option.\n\n## Target Audience\nIndividual gift-givers (age 20–60, urban/suburban residents), birthday hosts and party planners, event planners, and corporate buyers (HR/event teams, office managers) in a single city/metropolitan area initially. Customers value convenience, aesthetics, and high-quality artisanal food.\n\n## Value Proposition\nHigh-quality, artisanal mini-dessert boxes that are immediately giftable — combining curated variety, premium recipes, attractive packaging, and fast local fulfillment (including same-day delivery). Offers corporate customization (branding, messages) and subscription options for recurring gifting.\n\n## Key Features/Offerings\n- Curated mini dessert boxes: assortments of mini brownies, cookies, and seasonal/specialty treats  \n- Aesthetic, gift-ready packaging and personalization (notes, branded inserts)  \n- Local pickup and same-day local delivery (initial focus)  \n- Subscription monthly boxes for recurring consumers  \n- Tiered pricing and discounts for bulk/corporate orders, plus enterprise pricing and scheduled corporate deliveries  \n- Add-ons: custom branding, personalized messages, premium upgrades, dietary options (potential future offering)  \n\n## Business Model\nRevenue from direct-to-consumer single-box sales, subscription recurring revenue, bulk corporate contracts and event orders, add-on fees (branding, personalization), and delivery/pickup fees. Margins driven by pricing tiers, volume discounts, and efficient local production.\n\n## Market Positioning\nPositioned as a premium, local artisan gifting option between mass-market gift-boxes and single-item local bakeries. Competitive advantages are curated mini assortments, strong gift presentation, same-day local fulfillment, and corporate customization capabilities. Constraints to manage include product shelf-life, freshness, and production capacity in scaling.\n\n## Success Metrics\n- Monthly orders and revenue (DTC and corporate)  \n- Average order value (AOV) and contribution margin per box  \n- Corporate contract count and average contract value  \n- Repeat purchase rate / subscription retention  \n- Percentage of same-day deliveries met on time  \n- Customer satisfaction / NPS and unpack/unbox social shares  \n- Food cost percentage and production throughput utilization\n\nFeel free to continue refining your idea or ask any questions!",
                              "lineHeight": 1.5,
                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "500"
                            },
